ApexComponent.description: This Visualforce Component allows you to easily put a static map image into your Visualforce pages. Visit the Component Reference to get the details on the attributes available for this component. The Pages "GeocodeEmbeddedMap_goog" and "GeocodeEmbeddedMap_mq" included with this package are examples of an implementation of this Visualforce Component.
ApexComponent.label: StaticMap
